From: Len Brown <len.brown@intel.com>
Subject: tools/power turbostat: Print "nan" for out of range percentages
References: jsc#PED-14189
Patch-Mainline: v6.19-rc1
Git-commit: 8808292799b0eafd32d89e12a2536debcecaac11


Sometimes counters return junk.
For the cases where values > 100% is invalid, print "nan".

Signed-off-by: Len Brown <len.brown@intel.com>


Signed-off-by: Thomas Renninger <trenn@suse.de>
---
 tools/power/x86/turbostat/turbostat.c |   92 +++++++++++++++++++---------------
 1 file changed, 53 insertions(+), 39 deletions(-)

